lead_paragraph: Mired deep in last place in the AL East standings, the Tampa Bay Rays rallied late and kept the Boston Red Sox from moving within a game of the division lead.

headline.print_headline: Longoria's HR in 8th Rallies Rays to 4-3 Win Over Red Sox
